start a mvn project
$ mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.yourorganization -DartifactId=my-application1 -DarchetypeArtifacId=maven-archetype-quickstart -DinteractiveMode=falsea

compile the project
$ mvn compile

test the project
$ mvn test

package the project
$ mvn package

to install the package, into your home .m2 directory
$ mvn install

maven eclipse  
$ mvn eclipse:eclipse 

read more here https://community.oracle.com/docs/DOC-995861
